#: weblate/templates/trans/merge_instructions.html:8
msgid ""
"The exported Weblate repository can be shallow by default, so this workflow "
"works best from an up-to-date upstream checkout. Cloning from the exported "
"Weblate repository or using an outdated upstream checkout can fail even when "
"Weblate and upstream are in sync. See the FAQ below for details."
