#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1062
msgid "Choose additional projects where this component will be listed."
msgstr ""
"Wählen Sie weitere Projekte, in denen diese Komponente aufgeführt wird."

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1068
msgid "Use as a glossary"
msgstr "Als Glossar verwenden"

#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:1072
msgid ""
"Glossaries are different from regular translations but help keep track of "
